title: About
text: Ciao! I’m a Data Science master student in Rome. I love what I do, i.e., statistical modeling! I aim to combine my meticulousness of econometric analysis with the flexibility of machine learning. I focus on the application of data science with sequential data. I am an amateur musician and a jazz enthusiast, and a Beşiktaş JK fan. I like doing yoga and hiking in my free time.
